# ğŸ§  SENSE - Self-Evolving Network & Semantic Engine

**Version:** 3.0.1 (Fully Integrated)
**Author:** Todd Eddings
**Status:** Production-Ready with Autonomous Evolution
**Last Updated:** 2026-01-24

