## ğŸ“Š Monitoring & Observability

### Execution Statistics

```bash
sense --mode single --task "test" && \
python -c "
from sense.core.reasoning_orchestrator import ReasoningOrchestrator
orch = ReasoningOrchestrator()
print(orch.get_execution_stats())
"
```

**Output:**
```json
{
  "total_tasks": 42,
  "successful_tasks": 35,
  "success_rate": 0.833,
  "average_execution_time": 12.5,
  "total_retries": 8,
  "average_retries": 0.19
}
```

### Learning Trajectory

View learning progress over time:

```python
from sense.meta_learning.learning_trajectory import LearningTrajectoryTracker

tracker = LearningTrajectoryTracker(config)
tracker.visualize_trajectory(save_path="trajectory.png")
```

### Population Fitness

Track genome evolution:

```python
from sense.core.evolution.population import PopulationManager

pop = PopulationManager(config)
best = pop.get_best_genome()
print(f"Best fitness: {best.fitness}")
```

