### Development Setup

```bash
# Clone and install dev dependencies
git clone https://github.com/taeddings/SENSE.git
cd SENSE
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Run tests
pytest tests/ -v

# Type checking
mypy sense/ --ignore-missing-imports

# Lint
flake8 sense/
```

### Commit Guidelines

```bash
# Format: <type>(<scope>): <description>
git commit -m "feat(orchestrator): add retry logic to worker"
git commit -m "fix(bridge): handle timeout errors gracefully"
git commit -m "docs(readme): update installation instructions"
```

**Types:** `feat`, `fix`, `docs`, `refactor`, `test`, `chore`

